WEBVTT

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:33.456
there was this grown white guy
in the doorway blocking my way.

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:39.416
So I tried to walk around him,
and as I did that, he stopped me

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:41.240
and he was staring at me,

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:44.136
and he spit in my face, and he said,

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:45.376
"Get out of my way

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:48.656
you little black bitch,
you little Paki bitch,

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:50.600
go back home where you came from."

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:54.696
I was absolutely horrified.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:56.016
I was staring at him.

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:58.960
I was too afraid
to wipe the spit off my face,

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.976
even as it was mixing with my tears.